.DT
query_details_for
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
query_details_for

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
query_details_for -  This method returns the details for a specified type of money.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
class money_data query_details_for(string type)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^type%^RESET%^ - the money type to get the details for
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/money_handler.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method returns the details for a specified type of money.
It will return a class of the form:

.EP
.SP 5 5
({ forward short, reverse short,
.EP
.SP 5 5
   forward long, reverse long, composition,
.EP
.SP 5 5
   plural, adjectives, weight })
.EP
.SP 5 5

.EP

